channel.name: QVC Beauty UK
channel.title: Beautys Best Finds
channel.desc: Up your beauty game with our best finds in the industry, from favourite formulas to the latest releases. Whether you want to shake up your make-up or step up your skincare, find it here.

channel.name: QVC Beauty UK
channel.title: The Gift of Beauty
channel.desc: Find the right beauty gift for friends and family from skincare must-haves and make-up essentials to on-trend nail colours and beauty gadgets.

channel.name: QVC Beauty UK
channel.title: Liz Earle Naturally Active
channel.desc: Liz Earle is an award-winning British beauty brand renowned for creating naturally active skincare and bodycare products, which help to deliver real results for all ages and skin types.

channel.name: QVC Beauty UK
channel.title: Christmas Gift Ideas
channel.desc: Take the stress out of Christmas shopping and browse our marvellous selection of gift ideas to find the perfect present for someone special.

channel.name: QVC Beauty UK
channel.title: L'Occitane Gifting
channel.desc: Delight loved ones with luxurious L'Occitane gifts. Explore pampering skincare, fragrant bath treats and more-perfect for making every occasion extra special.

channel.name: QVC Beauty UK
channel.title: Elemis
channel.desc: Feast your eyes on our range of specially selected skin and bodycare collections from the luxurious Elemis range. Find the perfect gift to treat yourself or a loved one this festive season.

channel.name: QVC Beauty UK
channel.title: CIROA
channel.desc: Elevate your everyday self-care with wonderful beauty formulas from CIROA.

channel.title: Liz Earle Naturally Active

channel.name: QVC Beauty UK
channel.title: Floral Street
channel.desc: Discover Floral Street in our latest Beauty Cosmetics and Skincare show, a London-based fragrance brand inspired by young, urban British women, and famous for their contemporary floral fragrances.
